VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT associate_public_ip_address\s*=\s*true
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:associate_public_ip_address\s*=\s*true && MISSING:# intentional|# bastion|# jump|# nat
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects EC2 instances configured to receive a public IP address.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for EC2 Instance with Public IP.
